The Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking app brings insights to track commercial and service orders through various business milestones. Managers can use the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking dashboards to monitor the order journey, identify orders and tasks that require immediate attention, minimize order fallout risks, and improve SLA adherence.

Available in: Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions where B2B Communications Cloud is enabled
